descriptionHtml:
This is a retexture mod for jonwd7's Footprints at Skyrim
http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/22745/?

All human being's footprints are now high heel like...
So it's not a lore friendly mod, use it for your own taste.

Installation step:

1) Download [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/22745/?]Footprints
[/url]2) Extract bsa with one of the available tools and replace the textures, overwrite when prompt
2) re-package bsa and name it to Footprints.bsa
3) put the bsa file into your data folder

Done and Enjoy!
author: boblty
